      "text": "すずにゃんも愛ちゃんも甘いですね～\n会話も行動も全てここからお見通しですよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Suzu-nyan and Ai-chan are so naive~.\nI can see everything you’re doing and saying from here.",
        "id": ""
