      "text": "落とし穴の次は床が全てトランポリンの部屋！\nその部屋を抜けるとさらに……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "After the trapdoor‚ it’s a room where the entire floor is a trampoline!\nAnd after leaving that room……",
        "id": ""
