      "text": "あれ？　スタッフさんから内線？\nもしもし、こちらこころです。え、残り十五分！？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? A call from the staff?\nHello‚ this is Kokoro. What‚ only fifteen minutes left!?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 59.9663386228,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kkr",
      "speakerName": "赤崎こころ",
      "speakerNameEn": "Kokoro",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kokoro.png",
