      "text": "てってれ～！　最後はこころ自らおどかしに来ました！\nドッキリ＆イタズラ大成功～～！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ta-da~! I came to scare you myself in the end!\nPrank & surprise‚ a huge success~!",
        "id": ""
